‘‘Aṭṭhānametaṃ , bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo kañcikiñci 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='3', original='kiñci (ka.)', type='auto', previous=', bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo kañci '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='kañci'}
